04:43.717 --> 04:46.485
that trusted
third party function

04:46.487 --> 04:48.287
and it automates it.

04:48.289 --> 04:51.556
It puts it
into an open ledger
that is put online

04:51.558 --> 04:53.492
that is there
for anybody to see,

04:53.494 --> 04:56.061
so that every bitcoin
is accounted for,

04:56.063 --> 04:59.765
so that you know
that you're not getting
a counterfeit bitcoin.

04:59.767 --> 05:02.734
It's kind of remarkable
that this idea of bitcoin

