Banks and institutions

01:14:06.576 --> 01:14:08.142
associated with
the financial system

01:14:08.144 --> 01:14:10.578
are really starting to recognize

01:14:10.580 --> 01:14:13.214
that the payment system
underlying banking

01:14:13.216 --> 01:14:14.849
could be made more efficient

01:14:14.851 --> 01:14:17.618
by the application
of blockchain technologies.

01:14:18.754 --> 01:14:20.888
The blockchain technology

01:14:20.890 --> 01:14:22.757
underlying bitcoin

01:14:22.759 --> 01:14:24.692
has become something that

01:14:24.694 --> 01:14:27.595
a lot people are now
very, very interested in

01:14:27.597 --> 01:14:29.630
for all kinds of other uses,

01:14:29.632 --> 01:14:33.134
whether it's allowing
for derivatives
to be transferred

01:14:33.136 --> 01:14:34.969
or securities to be transferred,

01:14:34.971 --> 01:14:38.873
or all manner of financial
instruments to be transferred

01:14:38.875 --> 01:14:40.174
in complex, interesting ways.

01:14:40.176 --> 01:14:41.776
I think different companies

01:14:41.778 --> 01:14:43.811
are going to adopt
different strategies.

